OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry this
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunshine. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will be dry with
OL,8,Fmostly clear skies but some fog and
OL,9,Flow cloud possible later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FAny overnight fog and low
OL,12,Fcloud burning off through the morning
OL,13,Fto leave a dry, very warm and sunny
OL,14,Fday.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,17,Fdry, bright and warm on Friday, chance
OL,18,Fof a few showers. Cooler and and
OL,19,Fcloudier over the weekend with a
OL,20,Fchance of showers.
